# Sample Configuration for Market Alert Service

```json
{
  "market_alert_agent": {
    "monitoring": {
      "stocks": {
        "enabled": true,
        "watchlist": ["AAPL", "TSLA", "MSFT", "NVDA", "META"],
        "thresholds": {"price_change_percent": 5.0}
      },
      "crypto": {
        "enabled": true,
        "watchlist": ["BTC", "ETH", "SOL", "DOGE"],
        "thresholds": {"price_change_percent": 10.0}
      },
      "news": {
        "enabled": true,
        "keywords": ["earnings", "IPO", "merger", "acquisition", "FDA", "court", "lawsuit", "patent"]
      }
    },
    "deployment": {
      "telegram": false,
      "discord": ["#stock-alerts"],
      "slack": false
    }
  }
}
```

Save this as `config.json` in the market-alerts directory.